# =============================================================================
# 99_drop_all.gsql  —  FULL SCHEMA + DATA TEARDOWN (TigerGraph 4.2.x GSQL)
# =============================================================================
# WHAT THIS DOES: drops the entire iPerform schema and ALL of its data — the
#   graph, all 133 forward edge types (each reverse edge is dropped
#   automatically with its forward edge — reverse edges cannot be dropped on
#   their own), and all 60 vertex types. After this runs the catalog is
#   clean and a fresh CREATE reproduces the schema from scratch.
#
# ⚠️  WARNING: THIS PERMANENTLY DELETES BOTH SCHEMA AND DATA for graph
#   "iperform_insights_coaching_demo". There is no undo. Do not run against a live instance you are not
#   intentionally rebuilding.
#
# ORDER (TigerGraph rules): a global vertex/edge type cannot be dropped while a
#   graph still uses it, and an edge cannot be dropped while it is not first
#   detached from the graph — so we DROP GRAPH first, then DROP EDGE (forward
#   only), then DROP VERTEX. All at GLOBAL scope.
#
# RUN:
#   gsql docs/tigergraph_foundation/tigergraph/schema/99_drop_all.gsql
#   (or paste into a `gsql` session). Requires schema-admin privileges.
#
# RECREATE AFTERWARD (exact sequence — see CLIENT_SETUP_RUNBOOK.md "Reset /
#   rebuild the schema"):
#   1. gsql 01_vertices.gsql          # 60 vertex types
#   2. gsql 02_edges.gsql             # 133 forward edges (+ reverse edges)
#   3. gsql 03_create_graph.gsql      # CREATE GRAPH iperform_insights_coaching_demo
#   4. gsql ../queries/install_all_queries.gsql   # reinstall GQ-### queries
#   5. reload data (app "Run All Ingestion", or ../loading/run_all_loading_jobs.sh)
#
# SIMPLER NUCLEAR ALTERNATIVE (drops EVERYTHING in the TigerGraph catalog —
#   every graph, type, query, job, token, and all data — use only on a
#   single-purpose instance): replace this whole file with the one line:
#       DROP ALL
# =============================================================================

USE GLOBAL

# --- 1. Drop the graph (also removes its installed queries / loading-job bindings) ---
DROP GRAPH iperform_insights_coaching_demo

# --- 2. Drop all 133 forward edge types (reverse edges auto-drop with them) ---
DROP EDGE
